[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    149[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The problem statement is clinically accurate and emotionally compelling. The "study at position 47" scenario is real and well-known in radiology operations.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    150[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The technology section is genuinely educational: it teaches CNNs for medical imaging, the multi-model orchestration challenge, DICOM ecosystem complexity, and integration challenges without any vendor names. A reader on any cloud learns something valuable.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    151[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - FDA regulatory context is correctly framed: 510(k) pathway, per-indication clearance, 12-18 month timeline. This is accurate and sets realistic expectations.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    152[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The false positive management discussion is the most important operational insight in the recipe. The "15-20% flagged in the first week, ignored by day three" anecdote rings true and will save readers from the most common deployment failure mode.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    153[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - PACS vendor integration is correctly identified as the project-killing risk. The 3-6 month per-site estimate and the warning about cross-site variability are accurate.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    154[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The confidence threshold approach (conservative at launch, tune over time) is the correct clinical strategy.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    155[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Cost estimates are reasonable and well-structured (per-study breakdown by modality, monthly infrastructure costs).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    156[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The architecture pattern (DICOM Router → Study Classifier → Model Selector → Inference → Aggregator → Worklist) is clean and correctly separates concerns.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    157[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - VPC endpoint guidance is comprehensive and correctly lists all required endpoints for a private subnet deployment.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    158[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - BAA requirement is prominently stated.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    159[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The "Where it struggles" section is honest and clinically accurate (subtle findings, motion artifact, post-surgical anatomy, multi-finding masking).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    160[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Related recipes are well-chosen and the connections are clearly explained.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Implementation timeline estimates (3-4 months basic, 12-18 months production, 18-24 months with variations) are realistic for this domain.
